T02TD1621E:167a-1: sha ta tatva bya basth'a na /
T02TD1621E:167a-3: de kho na nyid drug rnam par gzhag pa //
T02TD1621E:167a-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1621E:167a-5: dpal ldan khyab bdag lnga yi dngos //
T02TD1621E:167a-6: ye shes mkha' 'gro la btud de //
T02TD1621E:167a-7: bla ma'i bka' bzhin nyer bsten te //
T02TD1621E:167a-8: de nyid drug 'di bdag gis bya //
T02TD1621E:167a-9: gsang rgyud 'phags pa gdan bzhi las //
T02TD1621E:167a-10: btus te slob ma blo zhan la //
T02TD1621E:167a-11: phan phyir dad pas 'di byas kyang //
T02TD1621E:167a-12: mkhas pas dpyad cing bzod par gso //
T02TD1621E:167a-13: rdo rje dril bu bgrang phreng dang //
T02TD1621E:167a-14: ye shes dang ni rnam bzhi la //
T02TD1621E:167a-15: bdud rtsi 'dod dang mchod rten gnyis //
T02TD1621E:167a-16: bsnan te drug tu shes par bya ;
T02TD1621E:167a-17: / dang po rdo rje bsdams pa ni //
T02TD1621E:167a-18: bkrol te lag pa gnyis brkyang nas //
T02TD1621E:167a-19: padma'i lag skor lnga byas te //
T02TD1621E:167a-20: pus mo g-yas g-yon steng du gzhag / lag mthil gnyis la bsgom pa ni //
T02TD1621E:167a-21: g-yas su nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang //
T02TD1621E:167a-22: g-yon du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dag / ma dang aa las bskyed par bya //
T02TD1621E:167a-23: de steng rdo rje dril bzhag nas //
T02TD1621E:167a-24: h'um dang aa las bskyed par bya //
T02TD1621E:167a-25: a'a li k'a li'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1621E:167a-26: thabs dang shes rab dngos su ni //
T02TD1621E:167a-27: rtogs te de nyid bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1621E:167a-28: de nas rdo rje'i de nyid ni //
T02TD1621E:167a-29: bsgom pa'i man ngag 'di lta ste //
T02TD1621E:167a-30: rdo rje'i steng gi rtse lnga la //
T02TD1621E:167a-31: rigs lnga'i lha dang sbyar bar bya //
T02TD1621E:167a-32: dkyil gyi rtse mor rnam snang mdzad //
T02TD1621E:167a-33: shar gyi rtse mor mi bskyod pa //
T02TD1621E:167a-34: lho rtser rin chen 'byung ldan te //
T02TD1621E:167a-35: snang ba mtha' yas nub tu dgod //
T02TD1621E:167a-36: byang du don yod grub pa bsgoms //
T02TD1621E:167a-38: byang chub sems brgyad shes bya ste //
T02TD1621E:167a-39: padma'i phyag dang byams pa dang //
T02TD1621E:167a-40: nam mkha' mdzod dang kun du bzang //
T02TD1621E:167a-41: phyag na rdo rje 'jam dpal dang //
T02TD1621E:167a-42: sgrib sel dang ni sa snying po //
T02TD1621E:167a-43: lha rnams brgyad po 'di dag ni //
T02TD1621E:167a-44: ji bzhin phyogs su bsgom pa yin //
T02TD1621E:167a-45: dbus kyi sgo nga lta bu la //
T02TD1621E:167b-0: ye shes lnga ni bsgom @167b par bya //
T02TD1621E:167b-1: de yi phyi rol phyogs bzhin //
T02TD1621E:167b-2: lcags kyu la sogs rnam bzhi bsgom //
T02TD1621E:167b-4: sgeg mo la sogs brgyad bsgom pa //
T02TD1621E:167b-5: rgyud las sbas nas ma gsungs kyang //
T02TD1621E:167b-6: man ngag don gyi sa shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:167b-7: 'og gi rtse mo rnam lnga yang //
T02TD1621E:167b-8: bcom ldan mkha' 'gro ma lnga ste //
T02TD1621E:167b-9: dbus rtse ye shes mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1621E:167b-10: de yi phyi rol phyogs bzhin //
T02TD1621E:167b-11: shar du rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1621E:167b-12: de bzhin drag mo byang phyogs te //
T02TD1621E:167b-13: ro lang ma ni nub kyi rtser //
T02TD1621E:167b-14: lho ru gdol pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1621E:167b-15: rdo rje de nyid lha mor bsgom //
T02TD1621E:167b-16: de ltar sum cu rtsa gcig ltar //
T02TD1621E:167b-17: rtogs te rdo rjer bsgoms nas ni //
T02TD1621E:167b-18: h'um gi dbyangs 'di blang byas te //
T02TD1621E:167b-19: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyes par bya//
T02TD1621E:167b-21: mdzes pa'i rdo rje gsor nas su //
T02TD1621E:167b-22: sems can thar pa la ni dgod //
T02TD1621E:167b-23: rnam par thar pa chos kyi don //
T02TD1621E:167b-24: rdo rje snying po 'dzin par bya //
T02TD1621E:167b-25: h'um h'um h'um ho ho ho //
T02TD1621E:167b-26: de ni 'khor ba gcod gyur te //
T02TD1621E:167b-27: nyon mongs mun pa bsal byas nas //
T02TD1621E:167b-28: bla med byang chub thob pa dang //
T02TD1621E:167b-29: ye shes snang ba thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1621E:167b-30: rdo rje de nyid ma shes na //
T02TD1621E:167b-31: byang chub dngos grub ring du spangs / rdo rje dag par ma gyur na //
T02TD1621E:167b-32: brgya byin mtshon cha rdo rje 'dra //
T02TD1621E:167b-33: de nas dril bu de nyid ni //
T02TD1621E:167b-34: nang gi nam mkha'i khams la ni //
T02TD1621E:167b-35: byang chub snying po gnas pa yin //
T02TD1621E:167b-36: mtshan nyid med par spang ba ni //
T02TD1621E:167b-37: bum pa shes rab bdud rtsi'o //
T02TD1621E:167b-39: sa bon brgyad las lha mo brgyad //
T02TD1621E:167b-40: shar du lha mo sgrol ma ste //
T02TD1621E:167b-41: na bza' dkar mo byang gi phyogs //
T02TD1621E:167b-42: nub tu m'a ma k'i shes bya //
T02TD1621E:167b-43: de bzhin lho ru sangs rgyas spyan //
T02TD1621E:167b-44: me yi mtshams su skul byed ma //
T02TD1621E:167b-45: rdo rje lu gu rgyud dbang ldan //
T02TD1621E:167b-46: khro gnyer ma ni rlung mtshams su //
T02TD1621E:167b-47: bden bral mtshams su rin chen sgron //
T02TD1621E:167b-48: lha mo de brgyad dbus su yang //
T02TD1621E:167b-49: shes rab pha rol phyin pa ste //
T02TD1621E:167b-50: padma rgyas pa'i spyan mnga' ma //
T02TD1621E:167b-51: gzugs rdzogs 'od dang ldan par bsgom //
T02TD1621E:167b-53: sngon bzhin sgeg mo la sogs brgyad //
T02TD1621E:167b-55: dbus kyi lce la ye shes te //
T02TD1621E:168a-2: rnam par dag pa'i dril bu 'di//
T02TD1621E:168a-3: sngags 'di dag ni bzlas nas su //
T02TD1621E:168a-4: phyogs brgyad dag tu len gsum dkrol //
T02TD1621E:168a-5: aom badzra ghande ra ni ta pra ra ni ta sarba buddha pra tsa li te pradzny'a p'a ra mi t'a /
T02TD1621E:168a-6: n'a d'a sva bh'a we h'um h'um h'um ho ho ho aa sv'a h'a /
T02TD1621E:168a-7: shes rab chos kyi dril bu 'di //
T02TD1621E:168a-8: sangs rgya thams cad blang byas nas //
T02TD1621E:168a-9: mi shes 'dam las bying ba yi //
T02TD1621E:168a-10: sems can sangs rgyas don du dkrol //
T02TD1621E:168a-11: de nyid sbyor ba dman na ni //
T02TD1621E:168a-12: dngos grub ring du mtshon pa ste //
T02TD1621E:168a-13: de nyid med pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i //
T02TD1621E:168a-14: glang chen dril bu dkrol ba 'dra //
T02TD1621E:168a-15: de nas bgrang phreng de nyid kyi //
T02TD1621E:168a-16: yang dag cho ga shes par bya'o //
T02TD1621E:168a-17: shel dang nya phyis mu tig dang //
T02TD1621E:168a-18: dkar po la sogs gzhan yang rung //
T02TD1621E:168a-19: zhi ba'i las la khyad par gsungs //
T02TD1621E:168a-20: gser dang dngul dang zangs ma dang //
T02TD1621E:168a-21: padma'i snying po rgyas pa yin //
T02TD1621E:168a-22: gur gum la sogs dri yis ni //
T02TD1621E:168a-23: byug pa'i ri lu dbang la smos //
T02TD1621E:168a-25: mi rus mngon spyod ces su gsungs //
T02TD1621E:168a-26: zhi rgyas dbang du mngon spyod la //
T02TD1621E:168a-27: bod tses ni las kun byed //
T02TD1621E:168a-28: de yi grang ni 'di lta ste //
T02TD1621E:168a-29: sngags sgrub pa la lnga bcu dang //
T02TD1621E:168a-30: dbang la de bzhin nyi shu lnga //
T02TD1621E:168a-31: zhi ba la ni brgya phrag ste //
T02TD1621E:168a-32: brgya rtsa brgyad ni rgyas pa'i yin //
T02TD1621E:168a-33: mngon spyod la ni drug cu'o //
T02TD1621E:168a-34: phreng thag dgu sgril byas pa la //
T02TD1621E:168a-35: mdo 'dzin nyis brtsegs shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:168a-36: g-yas pa'i lag mthil nyi ma la //
T02TD1621E:168a-37: a'a: yig dmar po bsgom par bya //
T02TD1621E:168a-38: g-yon gyi lag mthil zla ba la //
T02TD1621E:168a-39: h'um yig dmar po bsgom nas su //
T02TD1621E:168a-40: sa bon de nyid las bskyed pa ;
T02TD1621E:168a-41: / g-yas sor rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
T02TD1621E:168a-43: phreng ba gang yin dkyil bzhag ste //
T02TD1621E:168a-44: rdo rje padma snyim par sbyar //
T02TD1621E:168a-45: ri lu dgra bcom bsgoms nas su //
T02TD1621E:168a-46: phreng thag lha dgur byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1621E:168a-48: gong ma chos kyi sku ru bsgom //
T02TD1621E:168a-49: bgrang phreng de nyid bsgom nas su //
T02TD1621E:168a-50: sngags 'di yis ni byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1621E:168a-51: aom ya te ya ma h'a dzny'a na sarba buddha ma h'a bhe be ta //
T02TD1621E:168a-52: h'um h'um h'um ho ho ho aa sv'a h'a /
T02TD1621E:168a-53: chos kyi sku dang mchod rten la //
T02TD1621E:168a-54: dgra bcom bskor ba byed bsams te //
T02TD1621E:168b-0: mchod rten grib ma'ang @168b mi 'gong phyir //
T02TD1621E:168b-1: bsgyur log byas nas phreng ba bgrang //
T02TD1621E:168b-2: phreng ba de rnams bgrang ba yang //
T02TD1621E:168b-3: so so'i khyad par gyis shes te //
T02TD1621E:168b-4: zhi ba'i phreng ba mdzub la bzhag //
T02TD1621E:168b-5: de bzhin rgyas pa gung mo ste //
T02TD1621E:168b-6: srin lag la ni dbang du bshad //
T02TD1621E:168b-7: mngon spyod mthe chung shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:168b-8: sgrub pa'i lha gang 'gugs bsams te //
T02TD1621E:168b-9: mthe bong lcags kyis bkug par bsgom //
T02TD1621E:168b-10: de yang lha mo g-yon pas 'dren //
T02TD1621E:168b-11: g-yas pas lha rnams 'dren pa yin //
T02TD1621E:168b-12: de ltar dag pa'i bgrang phreng gis //
T02TD1621E:168b-14: de nyid med pa'i phreng ba ni //
T02TD1621E:168b-15: bud med rgyan gyi do shal 'dra //
T02TD1621E:168b-16: de nas ye shes de nyid ni //
T02TD1621E:168b-17: 'di ltar yang dag shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:168b-18: chos kun ye shes gcig pa la /
T02TD1621E:168b-19: khyad par ring thung gyur nas gnas //
T02TD1621E:168b-20: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-21: dri za dang ni lha min dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-22: nam mkha' lding dang mi'am ci ;
T02TD1621E:168b-23: / rgyal chen dang ni gang ba bzang //
T02TD1621E:168b-24: lto 'phye dang ni grub bum dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-25: mi dang mi min mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1621E:168b-26: byol song dang ni yi dags dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-27: dmyal bar bcas pa'i sems can dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-28: byol song gzugs kyi khyad par dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-29: phra mo sgo nga 'dzin sogs pa'i //
T02TD1621E:168b-30: de rnams g-yo ba thams cad dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-31: mi g-yo ba yi rnam pa yang //
T02TD1621E:168b-32: sa chu me dang rlung gi khams //
T02TD1621E:168b-33: phra mo gtso dang lo ma dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-34: rdo dang bong ba rtse mo sogs //
T02TD1621E:168b-35: thams cad ye shes snang bya yin //
T02TD1621E:168b-36: de yang sems dang ldan pa dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-37: sems pa med pa gnyis su 'dod //
T02TD1621E:168b-38: sems pa dang ldan khyad par ni //
T02TD1621E:168b-39: ye shes bye brag 'di lta ste //
T02TD1621E:168b-40: rgyal chen sum cu rtsa gsum dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-41: 'thab bral dang ni dga' ldan dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-43: tshangs ring tshangs pa'i mdun na 'don //
T02TD1621E:168b-44: tshangs chen dang ni 'dod chung dang //
T02TD1621E:168b-46: dge chung dge rgyas tshad med dge / sprin med dang ni bsod nams skyes //
T02TD1621E:168b-47: 'bras bu che dang mi che ba //
T02TD1621E:168b-48: mi gdung ba dang gya nom dang snang //
T02TD1621E:168b-49: shin tu mthong dang 'og min te //
T02TD1621E:168b-50: nyi shu rtsa gsum lha rnams ni //
T02TD1621E:168b-51: ye shes rags shing zab pa ni //
T02TD1621E:169a-2: de yang rgyal chen rigs bzhi nas //
T02TD1621E:169a-3: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed bar du ni //
T02TD1621E:169a-4: 'dod pa lnga yi ye shes dang //
T02TD1621E:169a-5: gong nas gong du zab pa yin //
T02TD1621E:169a-6: lha min ye shes khro ba ste //
T02TD1621E:169a-7: yi dags ye shes sme ba yin //
T02TD1621E:169a-8: gti mug ye shes byol song gi //
T02TD1621E:169a-9: dmyal ba'i 'jigs pas dub pa yin //
T02TD1621E:169a-10: mi shes ye shes rnam lnga ste //
T02TD1621E:169a-11: glen pa dang ni 'on pa dang //
T02TD1621E:169a-12: lkugs pa dang ni byis pa dang //
T02TD1621E:169a-13: ye shes can dang rnam pa lnga //
T02TD1621E:169a-14: bye brag tu ni shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:169a-15: gzhan yang gnod sbyin la sogs pas ;
T02TD1621E:169a-16: / rtsa ba'i rgyud las ma gsungs kyang //
T02TD1621E:169a-17: don gyi ye shes khyad par ni //
T02TD1621E:169a-18: rnal 'byor pas ni shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:169a-19: de 'dra'i ye shes de nyid ni //
T02TD1621E:169a-20: rnal 'byor gang gis rtogs gyur pa //
T02TD1621E:169a-21: de ni tshe rabs sa ya stong //
T02TD1621E:169a-22: sangs rgyas shes pas bskul ba'o //
T02TD1621E:169a-23: rnal 'byor gtsug lag las byung ba'i //
T02TD1621E:169a-24: ye shes de nyid mi shes te //
T02TD1621E:169a-25: phyi yi gtsug lag shes na yang //
T02TD1621E:169a-27: de nas bdud rtsi'i 'od de nyid //
T02TD1621E:169a-28: man ngag 'di ltar shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:169a-29: bhandha'am nya phyis la sogs pa //
T02TD1621E:169a-30: bdud rtsi lnga dang bsres pa yis ;
T02TD1621E:169a-31: / bdud rtsi'i 'od kyis bkang byas la //
T02TD1621E:169a-32: sngags dang phyag rgyas dag par bya //
T02TD1621E:169a-33: g-yas pa zla dkyil bsam pa la //
T02TD1621E:169a-34: bdud rtsi'i 'od kyis snod bzhag ste //
T02TD1621E:169a-35: g-yon pa rtse gsum phyag rgya yis //
T02TD1621E:169a-36: snod la reg nas sngags 'di brjod //
T02TD1621E:169a-37: aom ha ho hr'i: sv'a h'a /
T02TD1621E:169a-38: ha yis kha dog 'phrog pa dang //
T02TD1621E:169a-39: ho yis phyi yi dri ma bsal //
T02TD1621E:169a-40: hr'i: yis mthu yang 'joms byed pa //
T02TD1621E:169a-41: rim pa de ni shas par bya //
T02TD1621E:169a-42: de ltar log pa bsal nas su //
T02TD1621E:169a-43: 'di ltar yang dag sbyor ba bsgom// gzugs ni padma'i dbang phyug ste //
T02TD1621E:169a-44: rnam par snang mdzad dri chu dngos //
T02TD1621E:169a-45: ro ni rdo rje dbang phyug ste //
T02TD1621E:169a-46: sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor bsam //
T02TD1621E:169a-47: de 'og phyag rgya sngags kyis yang //
T02TD1621E:169a-49: sa bon sum las bskyed pa yi //
T02TD1621E:169a-50: g-yon pa'i mthil du zla ba bsgom //
T02TD1621E:169a-51: de dkyil bdud rtsi sa bon sum /
T02TD1621E:169b-0: bsgoms nas srin @169b lag mtheb rtser sbyar //
T02TD1621E:169b-1: bdud rtsi'i dkyil du phyag rgya de //
T02TD1621E:169b-2: bzhag nas rim pa 'di ltar bsgom //
T02TD1621E:169b-3: h'um las bskyed pa'i mthe bong ni //
T02TD1621E:169b-4: dbang chen sa gzhir bsgom pa dang //
T02TD1621E:169b-5: sum las bskyed pa'i srin lag ni //
T02TD1621E:169b-6: ri rab bzur bzhir bsgom par bya //
T02TD1621E:169b-7: srin lag rtser yang sum bsgoms te ;
T02TD1621E:169b-8: / bdud rtsi'i snying po gsum bzlas nas //
T02TD1621E:169b-9: lan gsum bdun ni bsgrub par bya //
T02TD1621E:169b-10: 'khor ba bdud rtsir dmigs nas ni //
T02TD1621E:169b-12: so sor gtor nas mnyes par bya /
T02TD1621E:169b-13: lce dang dpral ba spyi bo la //
T02TD1621E:169b-14: bdud rtsi'i thig le bzhag nas su //
T02TD1621E:169b-15: yi dam lha yang mchod bya zhing //
T02TD1621E:169b-16: dam tshig tsam du btung bar grangs //
T02TD1621E:169b-17: gang tshe rnal 'byor tshogs pa'i tshe //
T02TD1621E:169b-18: dbyangs 'di blangs nas gzhan la dbul //
T02TD1621E:169b-19: gzigs shing mdzes pa dam pa'i chos //
T02TD1621E:169b-20: 'di la the tshom byar mi rung //
T02TD1621E:169b-21: bram ze khyi dang gdol pa dag //
T02TD1621E:169b-22: rang bzhin gcig tu bsgoms nas gsol //
T02TD1621E:169b-23: rnal 'byor gzhan gyis blang ba yang //
T02TD1621E:169b-24: dbyangs dang phyag rgya shes bya ste //
T02TD1621E:169b-25: g-yas pa padma'i gdan bsgoms nas //
T02TD1621E:169b-26: g-yon gyi rtse gsum phyag rgyas blang //
T02TD1621E:169b-27: bde bar gshegs shing chos kyi mchog //
T02TD1621E:169b-28: dri ma med pa'i gnas 'di la gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam grol ba //
T02TD1621E:169b-29: de bzhin nyid de phyag 'tshal lo / de ltar man ngag rtogs nas su //
T02TD1621E:169b-30: bdud rtsi'i 'od la brten byas nas //
T02TD1621E:169b-31: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal bcom nas su //
T02TD1621E:169b-32: thar pa'i rtsi ru 'grub pa yin //
T02TD1621E:169b-33: de nyid med pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD1621E:169b-34: mdangs dang stobs dang longs spyod phyir //
T02TD1621E:169b-35: sred pa'i sgo nas 'thung byed na //
T02TD1621E:169b-36: sems can phal pa'i btung ba 'dra //
T02TD1621E:169b-37: de nas mchod rten de nyid kyang //
T02TD1621E:169b-38: yang dag par ni bsam par bya //
T02TD1621E:169b-39: nang bzhin nam mkha' dang 'dra bar //
T02TD1621E:169b-40: dngos kun stong pa nyid du bsgom //
T02TD1621E:169b-41: rang gi sems dang dbyer med pa'i //
T02TD1621E:169b-42: gdan bcas h'um yig 'dus par bsgom //
T02TD1621E:169b-43: de yi khams gsum 'jig rten ni //
T02TD1621E:169b-44: mchod rten gnas su bsgom par bya //
T02TD1621E:169b-45: sa yi khri 'phang zur bcu gnyis //
T02TD1621E:169b-46: dgug pa'i phyogs brgyad gling yin te //
T02TD1621E:169b-47: bang rim bdun du bsams pa ni //
T02TD1621E:169b-48: gser gyi ri bdun shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:169b-49: dril bu dbyings su bum pa ni //
T02TD1621E:170a-0: @170a * // lha gnas ri rab bsgom bya ste //
T02TD1621E:170a-1: bum rten 'khor ba gdung ba'i dbyibs //
T02TD1621E:170a-2: klu yi rgyal po nor rgyas yin //
T02TD1621E:170a-3: kha khyer rim pa drug ldan pa //
T02TD1621E:170a-4: 'dod ris lha rnams drug tu btags //
T02TD1621E:170a-5: dbus su srog shing yar bsgreng ba //
T02TD1621E:170a-6: bdag med chos nyid zad med bsgom //
T02TD1621E:170a-7: 'khor lo bcu bdun gyis brgyan pa //
T02TD1621E:170a-8: gzugs khams gnas bcu bdun du btags //
T02TD1621E:170a-9: chos kyi dbyibs pa yar 'phags pa //
T02TD1621E:170a-10: gzugs med khams bzhir shes par bya //
T02TD1621E:170a-11: de yi steng gi sgo nga'i dbyibs //
T02TD1621E:170a-12: rang gi sems ni sku ru bsgom //
T02TD1621E:170a-13: de la de bzhin gshegs pa dang //
T02TD1621E:170a-14: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
T02TD1621E:170a-15: rang gi slob dpon yi dam lha //
T02TD1621E:170a-16: bzhugs par dmigs nas rang sems dang //
T02TD1621E:170a-17: dbyer med bsgoms nas phyag byas nas //
T02TD1621E:170a-18: mchod dang bstod pa dbul byas na //
T02TD1621E:170a-19: bla na med pa'i go 'phang thog //
T02TD1621E:170a-20: gzhan du gzung 'dzin ma spangs par //
T02TD1621E:170a-21: dngos su rtogs nas phyag byas na //
T02TD1621E:170a-23: mu stegs phyag gnas lha rten dang //
T02TD1621E:170a-24: de nyid drug gi rim pa 'di //
T02TD1621E:170a-25: phyi nang gang du sbyor na yang //
T02TD1621E:170a-26: 'gal ba med cing dngos grub ster //
T02TD1621E:170a-27: ston pa thun mong bstan phyir ro //
T02TD1621E:170a-28: smri ti dzny'a na k'irti yis //
T02TD1621E:170a-29: slob mas zhus pa 'di byas pa'i //
T02TD1621E:170a-30: dge ba thob pa gang yin pa //
T02TD1621E:170a-31: de yis sems can sangs rgyas shog / de kho na nyid drug rnam par bzhag pa /
T02TD1621E:170a-32: rgya gar gyi mkhan po smri ti dzny'a na k'irtis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1621E:170a-34: // / pandi ta de nyid kyis bsgyur cing gtan la phab pa'o /
